<h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
<h3 id="open">Opening all or one</h3>
<p>Accordion does not control its Details children, your app does. You can allow all details to be open (the default behavior) or only allow one to be open at a time. This is as simple as removing the <code>open</code> attribute from all Details children except the one the user clicked.</p>
